title: [Hyacinthe's Magic Shoppe]
[Hyacinthe's General Store]
description: White silk-paneled walls rise from a glazed bamboo floor.  Just above a well-pruned lemon tree hangs a tattered merchant permit, and a billowing silk ceiling completes the picture.  An aqua-hued seaglass display and a heavy white granite counter stand side by side in the middle of the room.

White silk-paneled walls rise from a glazed bamboo floor.  Just above a well-pruned lemon tree hangs a tattered merchant permit, and a billowing silk ceiling completes the picture.  A whimsical apple green pushcart and a heavy white granite counter stand side by side in the middle of the room.
